title: 820-3115, pp3v3_s4 stuck on 0.4V
message:
You have missing xV_SUS rail, why do you check xV_S4 one?
Check S5 voltages and PM_SUS_EN.
Probably missing SMC_BATLOW_L, be sure to have correct charger.
